### Create auction
POST {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

{
  "title": "Xiaomi Redmi Note 14 Pro+",
  "Description": "Smartphone from Xiaomi",
  "startPrice": 3499.00
}

### Get users
GET {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/users

### Get auction
GET {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
### Get auction
GET {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
### Get auction
GET {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions/33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333
### Get auction
GET {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions/019cb450-d6aa-729d-bf2d-677050b5f8d6

### Get auctions
GET {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions

### Deactivate auction
PUT {{auction_site_api_HostAddress}}/auctions/019cb450-d6aa-729d-bf2d-677050b5f8d6
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

{
    "isActive": true
}

### Place bid as testuser1
